## Performance Targets

| Stage | Target Time | Current Performance |
|-------|-------------|---------------------|
| Image Upload | <1s | ✅ <1s |
| OCR Processing | <7s | ✅ 3-7s (Florence-2-base) |
| Hybrid Parsing | <8s | ✅ 5-10s |
| Data Merge (dual) | <2s | ✅ <1s |
| Database Save | <2s | ✅ <2s |
| **Total Single** | **<20s** | **✅ 10-18s** |
| **Total Dual** | **<25s** | **✅ 15-25s** |

---

## Error Handling Flow

```mermaid
graph TB
    Process[Processing Step] --> Check{Error?}
    
    Check -->|Camera Permission| CamError[Show Permission Error]
    Check -->|Upload Failed| UpError[Show Upload Error]
    Check -->|OCR Failed| OCRError[Retry or Manual Entry]
    Check -->|Parse Failed| ParseError[Show Partial Results]
    Check -->|Save Failed| SaveError[Show Save Error + Retry]
    Check -->|Success| Success[Display Results]
    
    CamError --> Fallback1[Offer File Upload]
    UpError --> Fallback2[Try Again]
    OCRError --> Fallback3[Manual Entry Option]
    ParseError --> Fallback4[Allow Manual Edit]
    SaveError --> Fallback5[Retry Button]
```

---

## Key Features in Process

1. **In-Browser Camera**: No page reloads, maintains state
2. **Dual-Mode Scanning**: Sequential front/back capture
3. **Hybrid Parsing**: Fast regex + accurate LLM
4. **Smart Merging**: Intelligent priority rules for dual-side cards
5. **Field Validation**: Prevents phone/zip confusion
6. **Auto-Save**: Contacts saved automatically after parsing
7. **Gold Theme**: Consistent visual design throughout
8. **Mobile-Optimized**: Touch-friendly camera interface

---

## Technologies Used

| Component | Technology | Purpose |
|-----------|------------|---------|
| **Frontend** | React + TypeScript | UI framework |
| **Camera** | getUserMedia API | In-browser camera |
| **Styling** | TailwindCSS + Custom CSS | Gold theme styling |
| **Backend** | FastAPI (Python) | REST API server |
| **OCR** | Florence-2-base | Text extraction |
| **LLM** | Qwen-2.5-1.5B | Semantic parsing |
| **Database** | Supabase (PostgreSQL) | Contact storage |
| **Hosting** | Hugging Face Spaces | Deployment |

---

## Success Criteria

✅ **Speed**: Processing completed in <20 seconds  
✅ **Accuracy**: Correctly distinguishes company/person names  
✅ **Accuracy**: Correctly distinguishes phone/zip codes  
✅ **UX**: No page reloads on mobile camera usage  
✅ **UX**: Clear visual feedback during processing  
✅ **Reliability**: Graceful error handling  
✅ **Feature**: Dual-side card support  
✅ **Design**: Premium gold aesthetic
